<view class="screen report-screen">
  <view class="section report-card">
    <view class="row between report-head">
      <view>
        <view class="title-lg">地块诊断报告</view>
        <view class="caption muted">2026-05-15 · PML 新模型展示页</view>
      </view>
      <view class="report-icon">R</view>
    </view>

    <view class="divider"></view>

    <view wx:for="{{rows}}" wx:key="label" class="report-row">
      <view class="report-label">{{item.label}}</view>
      <view class="report-value">{{item.value}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="title-md">自动生成结论</view>
    <view class="body conclusion">当前模型以 PML-V2.2a ETa 与 ERA5 ET0 构造 Kcact 标签，并统一到 ERA5-like 0.1° 尺度。七指标 LOYO pooled R² 为 0.765，说明在跨年份验证下能够较稳定地重建夏玉米生长季 Kcact 变化。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="title-md">说明书配图用途</view>
    <view class="body muted">这页适合放在中期说明书的“产品输出形式”小节，表达系统最终可以从遥感 ETa、ERA5 ET0 与七指标模型生成面向管理者的地块报告。</view>
  </view>
</view>
